                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
                        <p><strong>H&eacute;bergeur :</strong>GitHub, Inc.</p>
                        <p><strong>Adresse :</strong> 88 Colin P. Kelly Jr. Street, San Francisco, CA 94107, Etats-Unis
                        </p>
                        <p><strong>Contact support :</strong> <a href="https://support.github.com"
                                class="text-brand-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">support.github.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-brand-secondary">3. Directeur de la publication
                    </h2>
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
                        <p>Florian Gertner Kilian</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-brand-secondary">4. Contact</h2>
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
                        <p><strong>T&eacute;l&eacute;phone :</strong> <a href="tel:+33778407887"
                                class="text-brand-primary">+33 7 78 40 78 87</a></p>
                        <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@wizyx.me"
                                class="text-brand-primary">hello@wizyx.me</a></p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-brand-secondary">5. Protection des données
                        personnelles</h2>
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
                        <p>Le traitement de vos données personnelles est régi par la Charte de protection des données,
                            accessible depuis la section &laquo; Charte de Protection des Données Personnelles &raquo;,
                            conformément au R&egrave;glement (UE) 2016/679 (RGPD).</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-brand-secondary">6. Cookies</h2>
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-6 space-y-2 shadow-sm">
